  "title": "🍽️ Service Crew (Healthy Bowl Café Concept) | CBD Area | Up to $3,300 + VB",
  "description": "<h4><strong>About the Role</strong></h4>\n<p>Join a fast-growing F&amp;B group known for its wholesome, balanced meals and modern café environment. You’ll be part of a vibrant service team delivering great customer experiences in a clean and lively setting.</p>\n<h4><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Greet and serve customers in a friendly, professional manner</li>\n  <li>Take and process customer orders accurately</li>\n  <li>Handle cashiering and POS transactions</li>\n  <li>Maintain cleanliness and hygiene of dining and counter areas</li>\n  <li>Support opening and closing duties</li>\n  <li>Provide excellent customer service at all times</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>Requirements</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Positive, energetic, and customer-oriented</li>\n  <li>Enjoys working in a fast-paced team environment</li>\n  <li>Able to work weekends and public holidays as required</li>\n  <li>Prior service or F&amp;B experience is an advantage</li>\n</ul>\n<h4><strong>Work Details</strong></h4>\n<ul>\n  <li>Working Hours: 44 hours/week</li>\n  <li>Rest Day: 1 day per week (roster-based)</li>\n  <li>Benefits: Uniforms, staff discounts, annual leave starting from 7 days</li>\n  <li>Bonus: Performance-based</li>\n</ul>\n<p>EA License No: 23C1703 </p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R1762582 </p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p>",
